sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant CLI as rhai-cli
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OLM as OLM API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GH as GitHub (odh-gitops)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Admin,FS: Flow 1: Upgrade Readiness Lint (rhai-cli lint --target-version=3.x)
        Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --target-version=3.0
        CLI->>K8s: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC spec + status
        CLI->>K8s: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: DSCI spec (applications namespace)
        CLI->>OLM: LIST Subscriptions (redhat-ods-operator-*)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        OLM-->>CLI: Subscription + CSV versions
        CLI->>K8s: LIST CRDs (apiextensions.k8s.io)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: Available CRD types

        par Workload Checks (parallel across namespaces)
            CLI->>K8s: LIST Notebooks (all namespaces)
            K8s-->>CLI: Notebook resources
            CLI->>K8s: LIST InferenceServices (all namespaces)
            K8s-->>CLI: ISVC resources
            CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues
            K8s-->>CLI: Kueue resources
            CLI->>K8s: LIST RayClusters, RayJobs
            K8s-->>CLI: Ray resources
            CLI->>K8s: LIST PyTorchJobs
            K8s-->>CLI: Training resources
            CLI->>K8s: LIST DSPAs
            K8s-->>CLI: Pipeline resources
        end

        par Dependency Checks
            CLI->>K8s: GET ClusterVersion<br/>(config.openshift.io)
            K8s-->>CLI: OpenShift version
            CLI->>OLM: LIST Subscriptions (cert-manager, servicemesh)
            OLM-->>CLI: Dependency status
        end

        CLI->>CLI: Execute 37 checks<br/>Generate DiagnosticResults
        CLI-->>Admin: Table/JSON/YAML output<br/>(Pass/Fail per check with impact levels)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Admin,FS: Flow 2: Workload Backup (rhai-cli backup notebooks)
        Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli backup notebooks -n my-ns
        CLI->>K8s: LIST Notebooks (namespace: my-ns)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: Notebook resources

        par Dependency Resolution
            CLI->>K8s: GET Secrets (volume refs, envFrom)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
            K8s-->>CLI: Referenced Secrets
            CLI->>K8s: GET ConfigMaps (volume refs)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
            K8s-->>CLI: Referenced ConfigMaps
            CLI->>K8s: GET PVCs (volume refs)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
            K8s-->>CLI: Referenced PVCs
        end

        CLI->>CLI: Strip cluster metadata<br/>(uid, resourceVersion, status)
        CLI->>FS: Write YAML files<br/>(notebooks/, secrets/, configmaps/)
        CLI-->>Admin: Backup complete (N resources)
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over Admin,FS: Flow 3: Kueue Migration (rhai-cli migrate run kueue-rhbok)
        Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate prepare kueue-rhbok
        CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: Kueue resources
        CLI->>K8s: GET ConfigMap (kueue config)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: Kueue configuration
        CLI->>FS: Write backup files

        Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run kueue-rhbok
        CLI->>OLM: CREATE Subscription<br/>(kueue-operator, stable-v1.1)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        OLM-->>CLI: Subscription created

        loop Poll until CSV Succeeded
            CLI->>OLM: GET ClusterServiceVersion<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
            OLM-->>CLI: CSV status (Installing → Succeeded)
        end

        CLI->>K8s: PATCH DataScienceCluster<br/>(set Kueue: Unmanaged)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: DSC patched

        CLI->>K8s: LIST ClusterQueues (verify preserved)<br/>Bearer Token / TLS 1.2+
        K8s-->>CLI: Resources intact
        CLI-->>Admin: Migration complete
    end
